page.title: 10GEORGINA'S DIARY.
page.content: During the week I get up about 7.45. I get dressed and go downstairs to breakfast then I go back upstairs and wash my teeth and face. I get my school bag and on Monday, Wednesday and Friday I ride my bike to school in the summer and some of the Autumn and Spring with my friend. But on Tuesdays I go to music from 4 o'clock to 5 o'clock.On Thursdays I go swimming after school. The school bell goes at 9 o'clock in the morning and we leave school at half past three. After school sometimes I go horse riding.I have got my own horse and my mum owns a riding school. We keep the horses in the stables and on the floor we put straw. We give them hay and some food to eat, the food is called sugarbeet, bran and barley.We usually turn the horses out in the field for the night.
